---
import Logo from "../assets/images/Logo.astro";
import Link from "../components/Link.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layout/BaseLayout.astro";
import LLogo from "../assets/images/L_Logo.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <Section classes=" bg-white flex flex-col justify-center items-center ">
    <div class="flex justify-between w-full items-center">
      <a href="/"><Logo /></a>
      <Link classes="cta" url="contact">Let's have a chat!</Link>
    </div>
    <div class="grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6">
      <div class="overflow-clip"><h1 class="hero-text">Our studio</h1></div>
      <img
        src="/pointing-down.svg"
        alt="hand pointing down to scroll"
        class="absolute bottom-12 right-[clamp(1rem,_0.4rem_+_3vw,_4rem)] animate-bounce"
      />
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section
    classes=" text-white flex flex-col justify-center items-center  gap-8 bg-black"
  >
    <!-- <LLogo classes="fill-white max-w-[500px]" /> -->
    <p class="max-w-screen-lg text-center text-4xl">
      An independent creative studio based in Rotterdam. We take your brands
      through strategy, creativity and digital innovation.
    </p>
  </Section>

  <Section
    classes="   w-full bg-white  flex flex-col justify-center items-center  gap-6 "
  >
    <div class="overflow-clip max-w-screen-lg">
      <h2 class="">We’re all about your business goals</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-clip max-w-screen-lg">
      <p class="overflow-clip">
        We're all about making your business goals our top priority. When it
        comes to solutions, we don't just deliver; we serve up exactly what your
        business craves. Think of us as your digital matchmaker, connecting you
        with a broader audience, boosting your website's SEO game, smashing
        through those geographical barriers, and putting you on the global map.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section
    classes="indexCards text-white flex flex-col justify-center items-center  gap-8 bg-black"
  >
    <div class="overflow-clip max-w-screen-lg">
      <h2 class="">We’re good at</h2>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section
  classes="  indexCards w-full bg-white  flex flex-col justify-center items-center  gap-6 "
  >
    <div class="overflow-clip max-w-screen-lg">
      <h2 class="">Website Design</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-clip max-w-screen-lg">
      <p class="overflow-clip text-center">
        We combine aesthetics and functionality to create digital experiences
        that truly connect with your audience. Our user-centered design process
        not only boosts productivity but also drives revenue and growth,
        ensuring your company thrives.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section
  classes="indexCards w-full bg-white  flex flex-col justify-center items-center  gap-6  "
  >
    <div class="overflow-clip max-w-screen-lg">
      <h2 class="">Website development</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-clip max-w-screen-lg">
      <p class="overflow-clip text-center">
        We turn ideas into powerful, interactive websites. It’s about combining
        code and design to create sites that look great and work even better. A
        solid website boosts user experience, engagement, and business growth.
        Whether it's a blog or an e-commerce powerhouse, we know how to make
        your digital vision a reality. No fluff, just results.  
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section
    classes="   w-full bg-white  flex flex-col justify-center items-center  z-[9999] gap-6 "
  >
    <div class="overflow-clip max-w-screen-lg">
      <h2 class="">SEO Optimisation</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-clip max-w-screen-lg">
      <p class="overflow-clip text-center">
        SEO optimization is the key to making your website visible and attracting the right traffic. It’s about using the right keywords, creating quality content, and optimizing your site's structure to rank higher on search engines. With effective SEO, you drive organic traffic, increase engagement, and boost your online presence. No gimmicks, just strategic moves to get you noticed and grow your business.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
  
</BaseLayout>